    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "在设施的最深处，法尔艾斯开始了他的实验。\\n贝维特将魔幻炉中的魔力注入龙体内，\\n创造出了拥有黑暗魔力的波塞冬。\\n王子一行人与赶来救援的利弗\\n一同向强大的龙发起挑战。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "这里就是最深处了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这地方还挺宽敞的……\\n嗯？那是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "这是什么……好像……也不是水啊。\\n还闪着诡异的光……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "像是被吸过来一样……\\n莫非……这就是所谓的人造魔力？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "按理说，魔力本该是既看不见\\n也无法触碰的无形之力才对……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "做成这种形状是为了\\n便于控制魔力吗……\\n真是难以想象的先进技术……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "但这也太过分了吧……\\n汲取了这么多魔力，\\n难怪湖水和森林会变得异常……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "尤蒂尔！\\n他们两个在那里！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "法尔艾斯哥哥！贝维特！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，\\n你还真来了呢。\\n我很欢迎你们的到来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "法尔艾斯哥哥！\\n你之前就知道这处设施吗…",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "魔幻炉——即采集魔力\\n并将其实体化加以利用的\\n古代智慧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "依我所见，建造这处设施\\n是为了对早期的魔幻炉\\n进行性能测试。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "这里积蓄了庞大的魔力——\\n用来进行我的实验\\n真是再合适不过了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "好了贝维特，开始吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "呃……\\n这阵猛烈的风是怎么回事……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那个小鬼，到底做了什么！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "呜……大家找个东西抓紧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "要被吹飞了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "纳姆，抓紧我！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "嗯，好！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "魔力全都、被吸进去了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "好浓烈的瘴气……\\n甚至无法直视……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那家伙的身体\\n到底是什么情况……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "贝维特准备就绪了呢。\\n那么接下来就是这个……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "有什么东西从里面出来了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "可恶，又是黑暗魔力之龙吗！\\n接连不断地冒出来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不、不对……听这叫声，\\n是还保有一丝理智的龙。\\n但好像充满了愤怒……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "波塞冬",
            "context": "嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这头龙……\\n难道是黎布湖的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你没猜错，\\n这正是掌管湖中魔力的水龙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "难怪没在湖里看到……\\n原来你把龙抓来了这里吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "准确地来说，\\n我只是接管了这头被皇帝陛下\\n下令活捉的龙而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "莫尔托梅塞亚的命令！？\\n法尔艾斯哥哥，\\n你为什么要与魔神为伍！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "帮助我研究的是魔神\\n还是人类，我并不在意。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我和皇帝陛下\\n有着共同的目标。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210025_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "波塞冬",
            "context": "嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "法尔艾斯哥哥，\\n那孩子有危险！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯！？到底要做什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01",
                "100003_01",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210101_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "波塞冬",
            "context": "嗷、嗷、嗷……嗷嗷嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "龙被……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "被黑暗魔力吞噬了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "是那个孩子\\n在创造黑暗魔力之龙……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这么说，是你一直\\n在派龙袭击我们……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "嗯，是啊。我还在想\\n你们什么时候才能发现呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "啧，所以才有那么多龙\\n朝我们冲过来啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那家伙，竟敢骗我们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "好了，让我见识一下\\n全新的黑暗魔力之龙\\n有多大能耐吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "正好这里就有\\n很合适的实验对象呢……\\n就请你们协助我的实验吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "法尔艾斯哥哥！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呃……等等！\\n为什么！到底是为什么！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "艾德……不，贝维特……哥哥。\\n你也快住手吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "为什么我们\\n非得互相争斗呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "你叫我……哥哥吗。\\n无知还真是可悲呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "尤蒂尔！\\n危险！快躲开！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "尤蒂尔殿下，\\n抱歉我来晚了——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "利弗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "殿下，您没受伤吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "啊、嗯。谢谢你，利弗……\\n但你是怎么找到这里的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "是谢斯大人告诉我的。\\n她掌握了法尔艾斯大人\\n正在此地图谋不轨的情报。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原来，是谢斯姐姐……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "法尔艾斯大人，\\n请恕我冒昧谏言。\\n您已经误入歧途……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "您的才智应当\\n为阿尔贝里亚带来光明——\\n而绝非用在这种地方。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "呵呵，利弗，你真是没变呢，\\n还是那么喜欢说教。\\n不过……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "既然利弗也来了，\\n实验的舞台已经趋于完美。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "对龙注入超过其原本力量的魔力\\n会导致什么样的结果呢……\\n让我们快点开始验证吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_07_0066",
            "book_image": ""
